{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":907,"text":"Loneliness."},{"time":3475,"text":"All of us in this room\nwill experience loneliness"},{"time":5850,"text":"at some point in our lives."},{"time":8014,"text":"Loneliness is not\na function of being alone,"},{"time":10989,"text":"but rather, a function\nof how socially connected you are"},{"time":13672,"text":"to those around you."},{"time":15959,"text":"There could be somebody\nin this room right now"},{"time":18177,"text":"surrounded by a thousand people"},{"time":19738,"text":"experiencing loneliness."},{"time":23284,"text":"And while loneliness\ncan be attributed to many things,"},{"time":26961,"text":"as an architect,"},{"time":28716,"text":"I'm going to tell you today\nhow loneliness can be the result"},{"time":31677,"text":"of our built environments --"},{"time":33657,"text":"the very homes we choose to live in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37465,"text":"Let's take a look at this house."},{"time":39519,"text":"It's a nice house."},{"time":40764,"text":"There's a big yard, picket fence,"},{"time":43203,"text":"two-car garage."},{"time":46198,"text":"And the home might be\nin a neighborhood like this."},{"time":49559,"text":"And for many people around the globe,"},{"time":52104,"text":"this home, this neighborhood --"},{"time":55069,"text":"it's a dream."},{"time":57021,"text":"And yet the danger of achieving this dream"},{"time":59723,"text":"is a false sense of connection"},{"time":62606,"text":"and an increase in social isolation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65431,"text":"I know, I can hear you now,"},{"time":66912,"text":"there's somebody in the room\nscreaming at me inside their head,"},{"time":70263,"text":"\"That's my house,\nand that's my neighborhood,"},{"time":72578,"text":"and I know everyone on my block!\""},{"time":75056,"text":"To which I would answer, \"Terrific!\""},{"time":77379,"text":"And I wish there were\nmore people like you,"},{"time":80666,"text":"because I'd wager to guess\nthere's more people in the room"},{"time":83558,"text":"living in a similar situation"},{"time":85304,"text":"that might not know their neighbors."},{"time":87716,"text":"They might recognize them and say hello,"},{"time":90481,"text":"but under their breath,"},{"time":93416,"text":"they're asking their spouse,"},{"time":95243,"text":"\"What was their name again?\""},{"time":97593,"text":"so they can ask a question by name\nto signify they know them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103155,"text":"Social media also contributes\nto this false sense of connection."},{"time":107678,"text":"This image is probably all too familiar."},{"time":109700,"text":"You're standing in the elevator,"},{"time":111293,"text":"sitting in a cafe,"},{"time":112471,"text":"and you look around,"},{"time":114131,"text":"and everyone's on their phone."},{"time":117055,"text":"You're not texting or checking Facebook,"},{"time":119302,"text":"but everyone else is,"},{"time":120733,"text":"and maybe, like me,\nyou've been in a situation"},{"time":122976,"text":"where you've made eye contact,"},{"time":124884,"text":"smiled and said hello,"},{"time":127201,"text":"and have that person\nyank out their earbuds"},{"time":130534,"text":"and say, \"I'm sorry, what did you say?\""},{"time":133877,"text":"I find this incredibly isolating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136501,"text":"The concept I'd like\nto share with you today"},{"time":138709,"text":"is an antidote to isolation."},{"time":140703,"text":"It's not a new concept."},{"time":141978,"text":"In fact, it's an age-old way of living,"},{"time":144105,"text":"and it still exists in many\nnon-European cultures"},{"time":146609,"text":"around the world."},{"time":148517,"text":"And about 50 years ago,"},{"time":150419,"text":"the Danes decided to make up a new name,"},{"time":153560,"text":"and since then,"},{"time":154742,"text":"tens of thousands of Danish people\nhave been living in this connected way."},{"time":160470,"text":"And it's being pursued\nmore widely around the globe"},{"time":163862,"text":"as people are seeking community."},{"time":167445,"text":"This concept"},{"time":169818,"text":"is cohousing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173621,"text":"Cohousing is an intentional neighborhood\nwhere people know each other"},{"time":176898,"text":"and look after one another."},{"time":178908,"text":"In cohousing, you have your own home,"},{"time":181432,"text":"but you also share significant spaces,\nboth indoors and out."},{"time":185037,"text":"Before I show you\nsome pictures of cohousing,"},{"time":187383,"text":"I'd like to first introduce you\nto my friends Sheila and Spencer."},{"time":190499,"text":"When I first met Sheila and Spencer,\nthey were just entering their 60s,"},{"time":194455,"text":"and Spencer was looking ahead\nat the end of a long career"},{"time":197206,"text":"in elementary education."},{"time":198956,"text":"And he really disliked the idea"},{"time":200717,"text":"that he might not have\nchildren in his life"},{"time":203254,"text":"upon retirement."},{"time":207053,"text":"They're now my neighbors."},{"time":208498,"text":"We live in a cohousing community\nthat I not only designed,"},{"time":211536,"text":"but developed"},{"time":212724,"text":"and have my architecture practice in."},{"time":215200,"text":"This community is very intentional\nabout our social interactions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218510,"text":"So let me take you on a tour."},{"time":221496,"text":"From the outside, we look like\nany other small apartment building."},{"time":224735,"text":"In fact, we look identical\nto the one next door,"},{"time":227417,"text":"except that we're bright yellow."},{"time":230266,"text":"Inside, the homes are fairly conventional."},{"time":232676,"text":"We all have living rooms and kitchens,"},{"time":235213,"text":"bedrooms and baths,"},{"time":237135,"text":"and there are nine of these homes\naround a central courtyard."},{"time":240551,"text":"This one's mine,"},{"time":242450,"text":"and this one is Spencer and Sheila's."},{"time":244935,"text":"The thing that makes this building\nuniquely cohousing"},{"time":247596,"text":"are not the homes,"},{"time":249743,"text":"but rather, what happens here --"},{"time":252430,"text":"the social interactions that happen\nin and around that central courtyard."},{"time":256908,"text":"When I look across the courtyard,"},{"time":258618,"text":"I look forward to see Spencer and Sheila."},{"time":260657,"text":"In fact, every morning,\nthis is what I see,"},{"time":262717,"text":"Spencer waving at me furiously\nas we're making our breakfasts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267064,"text":"From our homes, we look down\ninto the courtyard,"},{"time":270138,"text":"and depending on the time of year,"},{"time":271954,"text":"we see this:"},{"time":273327,"text":"kids and grownups in various combinations"},{"time":276757,"text":"playing and hanging out with each other."},{"time":279145,"text":"There's a lot of giggling and chatter."},{"time":281479,"text":"There's a lot of hula-hooping."},{"time":284067,"text":"And every now and then,\n\"Hey, quit hitting me!\""},{"time":288361,"text":"or a cry from one of the kids."},{"time":290157,"text":"These are the sounds of our daily lives,"},{"time":293585,"text":"and the sounds of social connectedness."},{"time":296476,"text":"At the bottom of the courtyard,\nthere are a set of double doors,"},{"time":299891,"text":"and those lead into the common house."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302503,"text":"I consider the common house\nthe secret sauce of cohousing."},{"time":306383,"text":"It's the secret sauce"},{"time":307570,"text":"because it's the place\nwhere the social interactions"},{"time":310468,"text":"and community life begin,"},{"time":313014,"text":"and from there, it radiates out\nthrough the rest of the community."},{"time":319690,"text":"Inside our common house,\nwe have a large dining room"},{"time":322251,"text":"to seat all 28 of us and our guests,"},{"time":324857,"text":"and we dine together three times a week."},{"time":328158,"text":"In support of those meals,\nwe have a large kitchen"},{"time":330973,"text":"so that we can take turns\ncooking for each other"},{"time":333492,"text":"in teams of three."},{"time":334754,"text":"So that means, with 17 adults,"},{"time":338096,"text":"I lead cook once every six weeks."},{"time":340572,"text":"Two other times, I show up\nand help my team"},{"time":342974,"text":"with the preparation and cleanup."},{"time":344795,"text":"And all those other nights,"},{"time":346384,"text":"I just show up."},{"time":348423,"text":"I have dinner, talk with my neighbors,"},{"time":350899,"text":"and I go home, having been fed\na delicious meal"},{"time":353268,"text":"by someone who cares\nabout my vegetarian preferences."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359239,"text":"Our nine families\nhave intentionally chosen"},{"time":361601,"text":"an alternative way of living."},{"time":363835,"text":"Instead of pursuing the American dream,"},{"time":365979,"text":"where we might have been isolated\nin our single-family homes,"},{"time":368901,"text":"we instead chose cohousing,"},{"time":371467,"text":"so that we can increase\nour social connections."},{"time":374377,"text":"And that's how cohousing starts:"},{"time":376263,"text":"with a shared intention"},{"time":377941,"text":"to live collaboratively."},{"time":379449,"text":"And intention is the single most\nimportant characteristic"},{"time":382352,"text":"that differentiates cohousing\nfrom any other housing model."},{"time":386725,"text":"And while intention is difficult to see"},{"time":388794,"text":"or even show,"},{"time":390648,"text":"I'm an architect, and I can't help\nbut show you more pictures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393616,"text":"So here are a few examples to illustrate"},{"time":395706,"text":"how intention has been expressed"},{"time":398014,"text":"in some of the communities I've visited."},{"time":402459,"text":"Through the careful\nselection of furniture,"},{"time":404721,"text":"lighting and acoustic materials\nto support eating together;"},{"time":410056,"text":"in the careful visual location\nand visual access"},{"time":413212,"text":"to kids' play areas around\nand inside the common house;"},{"time":419398,"text":"in the consideration of scale"},{"time":421761,"text":"and distribution of social gathering nodes"},{"time":424572,"text":"in and around the community\nto support our daily lives,"},{"time":427913,"text":"all of these spaces help\ncontribute to and elevate"},{"time":431283,"text":"the sense of communitas"},{"time":432625,"text":"in each community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435073,"text":"What was that word? \"Communitas.\""},{"time":438117,"text":"Communitas is a fancy social science way\nof saying \"spirit of community.\""},{"time":443765,"text":"And in visiting\nover 80 different communities,"},{"time":446251,"text":"my measure of communitas became:"},{"time":448731,"text":"How frequently did residents eat together?"},{"time":452845,"text":"While it's completely up to each group"},{"time":454971,"text":"how frequently they have common meals,"},{"time":458406,"text":"I know some that have eaten together\nevery single night"},{"time":461469,"text":"for the past 40 years."},{"time":464298,"text":"I know others"},{"time":466239,"text":"that have an occasional potluck\nonce or twice a month."},{"time":469751,"text":"And from my observations, I can tell you,"},{"time":471769,"text":"those that eat together more frequently,"},{"time":473882,"text":"exhibit higher levels of communitas."},{"time":478170,"text":"It turns out, when you eat together,"},{"time":480990,"text":"you start planning\nmore activities together."},{"time":484200,"text":"When you eat together,\nyou share more things."},{"time":486397,"text":"You start to watch each other's kids."},{"time":488205,"text":"You lend our your power tools.\nYou borrow each other's cars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491144,"text":"And despite all this,"},{"time":493578,"text":"as my daughter loves to say,"},{"time":495119,"text":"everything is not rainbows\nand unicorns in cohousing,"},{"time":499281,"text":"and I'm not best friends\nwith every single person in my community."},{"time":503082,"text":"We even have differences and conflicts."},{"time":507414,"text":"But living in cohousing,\nwe're intentional about our relationships."},{"time":511685,"text":"We're motivated\nto resolve our differences."},{"time":515089,"text":"We follow up, we check in,"},{"time":517446,"text":"we speak our personal truths"},{"time":519564,"text":"and, when appropriate,"},{"time":521732,"text":"we apologize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523986,"text":"Skeptics will say that cohousing\nis only interesting or attractive"},{"time":528146,"text":"to a very small group of people."},{"time":530429,"text":"And I'll agree with that."},{"time":532648,"text":"If you look at Western cultures\naround the globe,"},{"time":535013,"text":"those living in cohousing\nare just a fractional percent."},{"time":538910,"text":"But that needs to change,"},{"time":541172,"text":"because our very lives depend upon it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544820,"text":"In 2015, Brigham Young University\ncompleted a study"},{"time":548527,"text":"that showed a significant\nincrease risk of premature death"},{"time":553280,"text":"in those who were living in isolation."},{"time":556905,"text":"The US Surgeon General\nhas declared isolation"},{"time":559323,"text":"to be a public health epidemic."},{"time":561424,"text":"And this epidemic\nis not restricted to the US alone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":567179,"text":"So when I said earlier"},{"time":569277,"text":"that cohousing\nis an antidote to isolation,"},{"time":573767,"text":"what I should have said"},{"time":575412,"text":"is that cohousing can save your life."},{"time":580840,"text":"If I was a doctor, I would tell you\nto take two aspirin,"},{"time":583823,"text":"and call me in the morning."},{"time":586536,"text":"But as an architect,"},{"time":587879,"text":"I'm going to suggest\nthat you take a walk with your neighbor,"},{"time":590934,"text":"share a meal together,"},{"time":593281,"text":"and call me in 20 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596010,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597312,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}